      *    * Determinazione pathname completo per il file di appoggio  *
      *    * in output                                                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-pth-fso-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione pathname per file in fase di com-  *
      *              * posizione                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione nome file completo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-pth-fso-pt1      .
           string    "/ZFAX/"    delimited by   size
                     w-det-pth-fso-nam
                                delimited by   spaces
                     ".XXX"     delimited by   size
                                          into w-det-pth-fso-pt1      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Pathname completo sotto /abd/asc            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AS"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      w-det-pth-fso-pt1    to   s-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-pat                to   w-det-pth-fso-pt1      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione pathname per file completato       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione nome file completo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-pth-fso-pt2      .
           string    "/ZFAX/"    delimited by   size
                     w-det-pth-fso-nam
                                delimited by   spaces
                     ".SUB"     delimited by   size
                                          into w-det-pth-fso-pt2      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
